snippet.title: The Last Faith - Release Date Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The Last Faith is coming to Nintendo Switch on November 15th! 

Experience a dark gothic pixel art adventure and learn what mysteries lie behind the gates of the City of Mythringal. Engage in merciless and precise combat as you fight your way through an array of beasts and monsters. 

#NintendoSwitch #TheLastFaith
